<h1>杀</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">shā</span><span class=alesi>(sha1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 杀 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 杀</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/kill" style="color:black;">kill</a>, <a href="/dictionary/slaughter" style="color:black;">slaughter</a>, <a href="/dictionary/murder" style="color:black;">murder</a>; hurt</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 6<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 6 strokes: <a href="/character/在" title="zai4: be at, in, on; consist in, rest">在</a>, <a href="/character/有" title="you3: have, own, possess; exist">有</a>, <a href="/character/地" title="de: earth; soil, ground; region">地</a>, <a href="/character/会" title="hui4: assemble, meet together; meeting">会</a>, <a href="/character/而" title="er2: and; and then; and yet; but">而</a>, <a href="/character/那" title="na4: that, that one, those">那</a>, <a href="/character/自" title="zi4: self, private, personal; from">自</a>, <a href="/character/年" title="">年</a>, <a href="/character/过" title="guo4: pass, pass through, go across">过</a>, <a href="/character/后" title="hou4: queen, empress, sovereign; (simp. for 後) behind, rear, after">后</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/木" title="Kangxi radical 75">木</a>&nbsp;75.2</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/采" title="cai3: collect, gather; pick, pluck">采</a>, <a href="/character/朝" title="chao2: dynasty; morning">朝</a>, <a href="/character/斗" title="dou4: Chinese peck; liquid measure">斗</a>, <a href="/character/织" title="zhi1: weave, knit; organize, unite">织</a>, <a href="/character/项" title="xiang4: neck, nape of neck; sum; funds">项</a>, <a href="/character/群" title="qun2: (same as U+7FA3 羣) group, crowd, multitude, mob">群</a>, <a href="/character/依" title="yi1: rely on, be set in; consent, obey a wish">依</a>, <a href="/character/属" title="shu3: class, category, type; belong to">属</a>, <a href="/character/限" title="xian4: boundary, limit, line">限</a>, <a href="/character/型" title="xing2: pattern, model, type; law; mold">型</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" title="List o